divs: Sighting DetailsI was on hwy 6 headed south of Ely Nevada. Stealth blimp passed by headed easterly. It was surrounded by a lot of jet fighters doing maneuvers. Nellis was having exercise named "Imminent Fury" at the time. I would have given a million dollars to have a good camera right then....
